to hear that.

30:11.853 --> 30:13.812
She's with Amanda Doherty.

30:15.465 --> 30:17.816
"With"?

30:17.859 --> 30:21.558
Involved with, sleeping with.

30:21.602 --> 30:23.212
With.

30:30.872 --> 30:33.005
Hey, Leon.

30:33.048 --> 30:35.834
Sorry I missed you earlier.
So what is it?

30:35.877 --> 30:38.445
