You're my daughter.

31:14.524 --> 31:16.613
But I am gonna ask you
to step down.

31:16.657 --> 31:17.788
What?

31:17.832 --> 31:19.094
Let Tim take over.

31:19.138 --> 31:21.531
-Leon.
-You're fired, Edie.

31:32.499 --> 31:34.109
How could you do that?

31:34.153 --> 31:36.633
Why?
Why would you tell Leon?

31:36.677 --> 31:38.766
Because I didn't want to lie
to our client.

31:38.809 --> 31:40.986
Or should I say
continue to lie?

31:41.029 --> 31:43.205
I have never compromised
this case.

31:43.249 --> 31:44.598
You know that.

31:44.641 --> 31:46.687
Look, I get it.
I get you're angry.

31:46.730 --> 31:49.081
I-I understand that,
but are you trying

31:49.124 --> 31:50.734
