to the ground?

31:50.778 --> 31:52.780
-Is that what you want, Tim?
-You lit the match, Edie.

31:52.823 --> 31:54.738
-These are your choices.
-Mine?

31:54.782 --> 31:57.741
Yes, exactly, my choices.

31:57.785 --> 32:00.005
So what are you,
like, a stepmom now?

32:00.048 --> 32:01.571
What?

32:01.615 --> 32:02.921
Enzo.

32:04.531 --> 32:07.142
That was just
a little something.

32:07.186 --> 32:10.624
He--he got an A.
We wanted to celebrate.

32:10.667 --> 32:13.627
Every single time I brought up
having kids with you,

32:13.670 --> 32:14.976
it was like a third rail.

32:15.020 --> 32:16.978
-I know.
-But I get it.

32:17.022 --> 32:19.067
You just didn't want to start
a family with me.

32:28.685 --> 32:29.860
Hey.

32:29.904 --> 32:31.514
-There you are.
-JULIA: Hey.

32:31.558 --> 32:33.125
Uh, I saw you canceled
our appointment.

32:33.168 --> 32:35.257
Yeah, yeah.
I-I did.

32:35.301 --> 32:36.650
Okay.

32:36.693 --> 32:39.044
Can I ask where you're at
with that, then?

32:39.087 --> 32:40.915
The egg freezing,
'cause hormones would be

32:40.959 --> 32:42.482
the next step.

32:42.525 --> 32:46.007
Maybe there are no next steps,
at least for now.

32:46.051 --> 32:48.488
-Okay.
-Sorry.

32:48.531 --> 32:51.795
I know you were dying
to show me all your ovaries.

32:51.839 --> 32:55.277
No, there's, uh--there's
always time for that.

32:55.321 --> 32:58.715
Thank you for being my doctor.

32:58.759 --> 33:01.980
It was nice to talk
to some--talk to you

33:02.023 --> 33:03.590
about all this stuff.

33:03.633 --> 33:06.985
Hmm.
So is this about Donovan or...?

33:07.028 --> 33:09.726
No, actually,
it's, um--it's not.

33:09.770 --> 33:13.121
I...I had the talk
with my dad,

33:13.165 --> 33:14.862
and...

33:14.905 --> 33:17.125
I'm not sure I can think
about my future

33:17.169 --> 33:20.041
until I figure out my past.

33:20.085 --> 33:21.738
How'd it go?

33:21.782 --> 33:23.697
Apparently
he's always known,

33:23.740 --> 33:26.004
and he refuses to discuss it
with me.

33:26.047 --> 33:28.006
Yeah, of course.

33:28.049 --> 33:30.573
Mm, I'm sorry, Julia.

33:30.617 --> 33:33.011
Everything always has to be
on his terms.

33:33.054 --> 33:35.013
Yeah, that's your dad.

33:35.056 --> 33:36.710
Why?

33:36.753 --> 33:39.017
Why does it always have to be
so complicated with him?

33:39.060 --> 33:42.759
Why can't it just be simple?
It was like that with my mom.

33:42.803 --> 33:44.631
Or at least I thought it was.

33:44.674 --> 33:46.937
I mean...
Who knows?

33:46.981 --> 33:48.852
Maybe I don't even know
who she was anymore

33:48.896 --> 33:51.812
or who I am, for that matter.

33:51.855 --> 33:54.162
You're still you, okay,
with all of the amazing

33:54.206 --> 33:58.340
and annoying qualities
that you've always had.

33:58.384 --> 34:00.168
You're a rock.

34:02.214 --> 34:03.824
You'll get through this.

34:10.048 --> 34:13.181
-ROXY: Whose shoes are these?
-Mine.

34:13.225 --> 34:14.661
Sorry.

34:14.704 --> 34:15.879
Why are they
by the front door?

34:15.923 --> 34:18.012
What, are we in Japan now?

34:18.056 --> 34:21.015
-Um...
-They're a hazard.

34:21.059 --> 34:23.104
-BOTH: Whoa.
-Roxy, what's going on?

34:24.888 --> 34:27.848
I'm such an idiot.

34:27.891 --> 34:30.242
I let him do it again.
I let him.

34:30.285 --> 34:32.200
-What are we talking about?
-Nick.

34:32.244 --> 34:33.723
What happened?

34:35.899 --> 34:38.076
I saw him.

34:38.119 --> 34:40.904
I went to confront him.

34:42.297 --> 34:44.604
And suddenly, it was like, um,
I was 16 again.

34:44.647 --> 34:46.606
You know, and I'm paralyzed,

34:46.649 --> 34:47.998
and I can't put
two sentences together.

34:49.696 --> 34:51.219
That was really brave of you.

34:52.699 --> 34:55.223
And he's so charming,
you know.

34:55.267 --> 34:59.358
And he looks at you,
and he--he tells you

34:59.401 --> 35:01.751
he can deliver you
to Nationals,

35:01.795 --> 35:05.625
and he can make
all your dreams come true.

35:05.668 --> 35:09.411
And he makes you feel like
a grown-up...

35:09.455 --> 35:12.719
and that you're not like
the other girls...

35:12.762 --> 35:15.025
and that you have
a real relationship.

35:15.069 --> 35:16.940
No, no.

35:16.984 --> 35:21.031
He is a controlling,
manipulative predator.

35:21.075 --> 35:22.642
You were a minor.

35:22.685 --> 35:24.731
The statute of limitations
has not run out

35:24.774 --> 35:26.341
You just say the word,
I will start the process--

35:26.385 --> 35:28.169
No.
It won't work.

35:28.213 --> 35:30.258
Okay?
It doesn't matter.

35:30.302 --> 35:31.955
He still has all the power.

35:34.219 --> 35:37.047
You know, in--in rehab,
they told me that I need

35:37.091 --> 35:39.180
to "speak my truth."

35:41.226 --> 35:43.880
What does that matter
if no one's gonna believe me?

35:43.924 --> 35:46.144
-Rox.
-ROXY: God.

35:46.187 --> 35:47.884
They're just gonna say

35:47.928 --> 35:49.669
all these terrible things
about me,

35:49.712 --> 35:51.192
which, by the way, are true.

35:51.236 --> 35:53.803
It's my fault.

35:53.847 --> 35:55.283
I gave them
too much ammunition.

35:55.327 --> 35:58.156
Hey, no, it is not your fault.
We believe you.

35:58.199 --> 36:00.332
And anyone who knows you
and loves you

36:00.375 --> 36:03.030
will believe you, too.

36:03.073 --> 36:04.988
You have to say that.
You're family.

36:13.388 --> 36:15.216
JULIA:
She would have loved those.

36:25.270 --> 36:27.881
You ever talk to her
when you come here?

36:27.924 --> 36:32.190
No, um, not out loud...

36:32.233 --> 36:36.237
but to myself,
private conversation.

36:36.281 --> 36:40.241
It try to be private,
but I just can't help myself.

36:40.285 --> 36:43.766
I end up sitting here babbling
like a crazy person.

36:48.858 --> 36:51.209
Dad, we have to be able
to talk about this.

36:51.252 --> 36:54.386
I can't just pretend like
I don't know what I know...

36:56.170 --> 36:59.217
Even though you want me to.

36:59.260 --> 37:01.784
I need to know what happened.

37:01.828 --> 37:04.787
You need to tell me
what happened.

37:06.441 --> 37:09.052
There isn't--
there isn't a lot to tell.

37:09.096 --> 37:13.361
Uh, your mother and I were
going through a rough time,

37:13.405 --> 37:17.887
and, um...she had a fling.

37:17.931 --> 37:20.760
And she assured me
that it was a one-time thing.

37:20.803 --> 37:22.979
And I believed her.

37:26.287 --> 37:28.855
That's it?

37:28.898 --> 37:30.813
You have to know
more than that.

37:30.857 --> 37:33.294
No, I-I didn't want
to know more.

37:33.338 --> 37:38.256
You know, it didn't matter
to me that you weren't mine.

37:38.299 --> 37:41.302
