You lied to me.

37:48.483 --> 37:50.180
I wanted to protect you.

37:50.224 --> 37:52.008
Did you?

37:52.052 --> 37:54.315
Or did you want to
protect yourself?

37:54.359 --> 37:56.274
-Julia, please--
-Dad.

37:58.580 --> 38:01.583
I...I need more.

38:01.627 --> 38:04.412
I need to know more.

38:04.456 --> 38:08.198
